31
00:01:25,552 --> 00:01:28,553
Saitama: Hey, hold up.
Do I know you, or--

32
00:01:28,555 --> 00:01:31,223
bakuzan: Shut your face!
This time around,

33
00:01:31,291 --> 00:01:33,358
bakuzan the monster
will be the victor!

34
00:01:33,360 --> 00:01:35,760
My deathblows are
about to rain down upon you!

35
00:01:35,830 --> 00:01:38,030
Art of darkness hell killer!

36
00:01:38,098 --> 00:01:41,366
Demon sweeper low kick!

37
00:01:41,435 --> 00:01:43,268
¶

38
00:01:44,905 --> 00:01:46,571
saitama: You guys, too, huh?

39
00:01:46,573 --> 00:01:49,041
Bakuzan: I can't believe
you're still standing.

40
00:01:49,109 --> 00:01:51,510
Impressive,
but, after that blow,

41
00:01:51,578 --> 00:01:53,912
